'''''Cape Town Affair''' ni''  filime y'ubutasi yakozwe na 20 Century Fox kuri Studiyo ya Killarney muri Afrika yepfo iyoborwa na RobertD. Webb muri 1967. Muri iyi filime hagaragaramo Claire Trevor, James Brolin, na Jacqueline Bisset. Nibisubirwamo by'amafoto 1953 ''[[:en:Pickup_on_South_Street|Pickup on South Street]]''.<ref>CAPE TOWN AFFAIR, The Monthly Film Bulletin; London Vol. 36, Iss. 420,  (Jan 1, 1969): 8.</ref>Nibwo bwa mbere Brolin yakinnye. We na Bisset bombi bagiranye amasezerano na Fox. Nyuma yaje kuvuga ati "Sinigeze nkunda cyane ariko twe [we na Bisset] ntabwo twari babi." <ref>BIDING HIS TIME: James Brolin Looking for Role Outside Weekly TV Rut
Murphy, Mary B. Los Angeles Times 2 Sep 1970: h17.</ref>

